'''Achamanam''' ('''achamana''', '''achmana''') is one of the most important [[rituals]] in the [[Hinduism|Hindu]] tradition. It is a purification ritual that is believed to cure all physical and mental illnesses.<ref>http://www.ibiblio.org/sripedia/ebooks/sandhya/yv/achamanam-n.html</ref> 

